{"tid":721391,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後個腦係咪裝屎？連Printer換紙都唔識換！","createTime":"2018-06-28T16:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:26:16.000Z","uid":19334,"like":40,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3586c35879c73677c1ce564deaf2ffd0188c67c4","tid":721391,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"話說今日番工有好多Admin野要處理，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要用大量白紙(Both A3 &amp; A4 size)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁印E-mail印Letter呢d不嬲都係搵D煙腸黎做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我叫完隻90後送完文件好快D番黎整，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日整唔哂唔好走（其實deadline有排），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住成件事交比佢之後我就唔洗跟啦（手板眼見功夫），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知7分26秒之後佢就叩我門，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以為佢咁快整完啦（起碼整一日），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢同我講部Printer印唔到A3 Size，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一野打開個Tray發現左......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/000323_b621b984db67a01cb91cb7710b118481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F000323_b621b984db67a01cb91cb7710b118481.jpg&h=647a4a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬你係咪咁痴線，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係豈有此理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後比我鬧完一輪出左封Warning 比佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83e043e347a10c4fabb910f223078c71964afd6","tid":721391,"uid":19108,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"又係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 流G好波"},{"pid":"f6be7a8ba52874de8911faabd199732869676cec","tid":721391,"uid":187076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"有創意"},{"pid":"6e6279b8e6ea8915e0bd5fbd2743699d887212e0","tid":721391,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83e043e347a10c4fabb910f223078c71964afd6","tid":721391,"uid":19108,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"又係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 流G好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"CHING HO BALL"},{"pid":"202938bdb30ecb8cf6ff9561dd44f470cc23efbb","tid":721391,"uid":52073,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"今次有埋圖，幾好"},{"pid":"09579e9e89dc4b1b902a8a201a04d1d774d5dfbb","tid":721391,"uid":104035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以畀少少誠意同創意"},{"pid":"7621a19db8f9ce9460ba1e18fccc2051d3feb66c","tid":721391,"uid":17545,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"抄post 垃圾"},{"pid":"11e00098ba5566dc54c0ac2572f122489fec458d","tid":721391,"uid":32899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"樓豬點睇德國收檔"},{"pid":"73d56ec754ed8af853c7730d24e2f79a15ba13a0","tid":721391,"uid":73351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"有圖，幾好笑<br />\n<br />\n樓主繼續加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  九十後真係唔鬧唔得"},{"pid":"739728bf4badcf324e83b99de56009a843834f93","tid":721391,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"系米以為好似咖啡機咁成個capsule 放入去<img src=\"/asset